{"tid":164554,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"半夜聽到隔離屋啲怪聲","createTime":"2017-03-20T17:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T20:49:49.000Z","uid":31242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cad7ae24093637ecd6cfb297ace6d1ef7670078","tid":164554,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"訓訓下突然比隔離屋一啲好似拉凳係地下磨擦發出嘅聲音嘈醒左<br />\n<br />\n本來都無野,但個聲斷斷續續幾秒一下持續左半粒鐘有多<br />\n<br />\n半夜搬枱搬凳搞半粒鐘我都驚驚地<br />\n依家越聽果種聲就越似有條友係度哀號/慘叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再聽真啲又有啲似係度嘔/喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到我淆淆地訓唔著上黎開個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adabec741947323bcb0593eac32f24d93c792a5a","tid":164554,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:44:27.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"35f7beee2e46451f06ff08e0bda1b95c813ae464","tid":164554,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"係我"},{"pid":"cd84ad7d931027d9fffff31885d8b3b5c33a235c","tid":164554,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:45:04.000Z","msg":"巴打，我啱啱都開左個拉櫈post"},{"pid":"8cfaae243dcfd9738842b621bdbd18b1adec0583","tid":164554,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:46:25.000Z","msg":"屌佢仲係度叫緊唔知乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大聲到仆街,隔牆都勁清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n越聽越似係啲人飲大左係度又喊又嘔嘅呻吟聲...<br />\n<br />\n屌啲呻吟聲(唔係女人淫叫果種) 真係聽到好撚心寒"},{"pid":"cd47f167ec273a331ff9e82de5f57b2f4eac85fe","tid":164554,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"報警先"},{"pid":"cc6dfd56bcc41b54b5bfa4bd880b7417eebd4a23","tid":164554,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:50:11.000Z","msg